Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.02,0:24:30.61,Meshi_EDCN2,,66,0,22,,{\an7\frz-90\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK}振作一些吧 搖晃的雙腿用上全力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.02,0:24:34.69,Meshi_EDCN2,,66,0,22,,{\an7\frz-90\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK}嘴裡哼著以往的風向標
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.69,0:24:38.24,Meshi_EDCN2,,66,0,22,,{\an7\frz-90\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK}有些惱火難以觸及的距離
